feedback.help-us-improve: Āwhinatia mātou ki te whakapai ake
feedback.help-content-goes-here: Ka noho te ihirangi āwhina ki konei.
feedback.thanks-for-helping-onetime-secret-improv: Ngā mihi mō tō āwhina ki a Onetime Secret ki te whakapai ake. He mea nui tēnei.
feedback.weve-built-this-tool-to-help-you-share-s: Kua hangaia e mātou tēnei taputapu hei āwhina i a koe ki te tuari mōhiohio tairongo i runga i te haumaru, ā, he mea nui ō wheako ao-tūturu mō te arotahi i ā mātou mahi. Ka āwhina i a mātou ki te whakatau he aha te mahi ā muri ake nei me te pēhea te whakapai ake i te ratonga mō te katoa.
feedback.hey-there-thanks-for-stopping-by-our-fee: Tēnā koe, ngā mihi mō tō toro mai ki tā mātou whārangi urupare. Ehara tō kōrero i te mea pōwhiri noa - he mea nui.
feedback.a-note-from-delano-founder-of-onetime-se: He tuhipoka mai i a Delano, kaiwhakarewa o Onetime Secret
